			<title><![CDATA[Senior Mobile UX Designer]]></title>
			<department><![CDATA[Product]]></department>
			<team><![CDATA[]]></team>
			<url><![CDATA[http://wattpad.theresumator.com/apply/Wwa7B2/Senior-Mobile-UX-Designer.html]]></url>
			<city><![CDATA[Toronto]]></city>
			<state><![CDATA[Ontario]]></state>
			<country><![CDATA[Canada]]></country>
			<postalcode><![CDATA[M2N 6K1]]></postalcode>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>
We&#39;re looking for a creative, talented application designer with proven experience in designing consumer applications for mobile devices. As our Senior Mobile UX Designer, you will work with a team of designers and developers to help us create the best application for connecting readers with stories that they love. Your creative skills allow you to generate multiple approaches to an interaction, and your technical skills allow you to clearly communicate how the interaction will look and feel through prototypes of varying fidelity. You should have strong opinions about which mobile products are great, which aren&#39;t so great, and be able to explain why you feel that way.</p>
<p>
What you will be doing:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Own the interaction design and user experience of our mobile applications, with an initial focus on the iOS and Android products</li>
<li>
Generate design specifications, task flows, wireframes, mockups and prototypes which focus on delivering a market leading user experience for reading, discovering, sharing and writing stories</li>
<li>
Work with the mobile product manager to set a roadmap, select technologies, and prioritize features and fixes in order to deliver the best user experience possible</li>
<li>
Work with the product visual designer to build a strong visual language for our mobile applications</li>
<li>
Collaborate with the brand designer and marketing team to ensure the Wattpad brand evolves in ways that are consistent with the product designs</li>
<li>
Collaborate with the Senior Web Experience Designer to produce a mobile-optimized web presence which is consistent with our applications</li>
<li>
Collaborate with peers at companies within the Union Square and Khosla Venture portfolios to grow your skills and understanding of product experience design</li>
<li>
Grow your influence and Wattpad&#39;s mindshare as a leader within the mobile design community</li>
<li>
Grow into a position of design and experience leadership at Wattpad</li>
</ul>
<p>
What we&#39;re looking for:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience working with small teams that ship software to users</li>
<li>
Experience designing for iOS, Android and mobile web browsers</li>
<li>
Relevant work or educational background in one or more of the fields of: user experience research and design, interaction design, information design, visual design</li>
<li>
Some experience and understanding in mobile web or app prototyping or development</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
