			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>Head of Community</strong></p>
<p>
As Wattpad&rsquo;s Head of Community you will ensure our 15,000,000 engaged readers and writers continue to be delighted by our product and a driving force behind new product initiatives and our evolution.</p>
<p>
You will support the needs of our community and advocate for them as our internal champion and you will evangelize our platform to the global reader and writer community.</p>
<p>
You know that every interaction counts, and you know what it takes to make users happy. You love people and their stories, you&rsquo;re passionate about Wattpad and you believe in our mission to enrich lives through stories.</p>
<p>
What you will be doing:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Outline, execute and measure amazing community initiatives that drive participation, engagement and happiness</li>
<li>
Lead our talented team of Community Engagement Specialists in their efforts to support and delight our users with exceptional client service, moderation and technical support</li>
<li>
Champion our Wattpad Ambassador program--- they are our super-evangelists, you will build a program that leverages our Ambassador volunteers as our community continues to grow</li>
<li>
Advocate for all users&rsquo; by clearly defining moderation &ldquo;tone and timbre&rdquo;, ensuring policies are clearly defined and followed by the Wattpad community as we strive to be inclusive, supportive, nurturing and generous</li>
<li>
Work across Wattpad teams (product, engineering, content and marketing) to communicate users&rsquo; needs and champion community priorities</li>
<li>
Identify ways to automate and streamline processes related to community support and moderation</li>
<li>
Monitor and measure our success in serving our community as it relates to superior support, retention and engagement</li>
<li>
Evangelize Wattpad stories online, offline and within Wattpad!</li>
</ul>
<p>
What we&#39;re looking for:</p>
<ul>
<li>
You have a strong and proven track record in communicating, motivating supporting and engaging people online</li>
<li>
You are results-driven with very high client service standards -- you always go the extra mile to guarantee first-class service and support</li>
<li>
You live online and navigate it with enviable ease</li>
<li>
You are patient, friendly, compassionate and genuinely love to help others</li>
<li>
You are an unflappable problem-solver</li>
<li>
You are a master of diplomacy with a high emotional intelligence --- you read people like a book!</li>
<li>
You create efficiencies wherever you can and love creating memorable experiences</li>
<li>
You have a BA or BS and an aptitude for psychology, sociology, political science or the humanities in general</li>
<li>
Simply put: <em><strong>You get people!</strong></em></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
