<li>
Work closely with the product team to ensure product consistency over multiple platforms</li>
<li>
Collaborate with other product managers, community engagement managers and stakeholders to co-ordinate and support each other&#39;s efforts.</li>
<li>
Evaluate and prioritize the severity of support issues.</li>
</ul>
