<ul>
<li>
Degree in Computer Science or Business</li>
<li>
At least 2 to 3 years experience in a similar role</li>
<li>
Experience working with designers or developers on a team that has shipped multiple software milestones to users</li>
<li>
Having strong opinions about what makes great products, and sharing/debating them with your team</li>
<li>
Ability to break down a complex project into manageable tasks and prioritize them</li>
<li>
Strong visual sensibilities, and an understanding of what makes a good user experience</li>
<li>
Experience with web or mobile technologies</li>
